title: HOLLYWOOD Studio With 1 Month Free | New Appliances
posting_body: ['1 MONTH FREE ON', 'A 14 MONTH LEASE TERM', "Located at 1245 Vine St, in Hollywood's heart, The Villa Elaine is an impressive historic building.", 'Built in 1925, the brick facade, curved windows, and lush interior courtyard are striking and beautiful.', 'These carefully renovated apartments are historically reminiscent while affording the functionality and convenience of new construction.', "Each finish was selected to reflect the property's original charm vintage-style fixtures, navy blue shaker cabinets, open shelving, and subway tiles-", 'and beautiful new flooring throughout.', 'show contact info', '<URL>', '1245 Vine Street, Los Angeles, CA 90038', 'APARTMENT FEATURES:', '- Custom Kitchen Cabinets', '- Marble-esque Counters', '- New Tiled Backsplash', '- All New Appliances', '- Hand-crafted Built in Shelving', '- All New Flooring', '- Lots of Light', '- Spacious Floorplans', '- Walk-in Closets', '- All New Bathrooms', '- New Ceiling Fans', '- New Designer Light Fixtures', '- Crown Molding', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES:', '- Courtyard', '- On-Site Laundry', '- Resident Lounge', '- Elevator', 'LOCATION BENEFITS:', 'Nearby Freeways: 101, 110', 'Restaurants: Katsuya, Delphine, Felix', 'Entertainment:', 'Mann Chinese Theater, Pantages Theater', 'Close Shopping: Hollywood and Highland Mall', 'Schools: Musicians Institute', 'PET POLICY:', 'Cats and Dogs Welcome.', 'Additional Fees and Deposit May Apply.', 'Call for Details and Restrictions.', 'Interior photos may not be of exact apartment.', 'Square Footage is Approximate.']
